</section>

<section class="bottom-cta">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Traeger down? Call today.</h2>
    <p>Same-day across LA, OC, Ventura. $120 outdoor diagnostic waived with repair. BHGS #A49573, EPA 608 Universal #1346255700410. Phones answered 24/7.</p>
    <div class="cta-row">
      <a href={phoneHref} class="btn-primary">☎ Call {phone}</a>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn-secondary">Book Online</a>
